keepConnect.name: Duro si asopọ
keepConnect.helperText: Ti o ba tẹ lori ọna asopọ ibẹrẹ, lẹhinna tọju ọna asopọ naa. Eyi nilo akiyesi pe ọna asopọ naa yoo tun wo ni igbagbogbo lẹhin ti o ba ge asopọ.
